item.title: CVE-2018-17542|2024-09-16T18:54:20.899Z -- oaklouds -- mailsherlock
item.description: SQL Injection exists in MailSherlock before 1.5.235 for OAKlouds allows an unauthenticated user to extract the subjects of the emails of other users within the enterprise via the select_mid parameter in an letgo.cgi request.
